BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 347.35 Td (represents.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 72 319.80 Td (V. Past International Action) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 295.15 Td (The international community has not been silent on Protecting Children's Right to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 280.65 Td (Education in Emergencies and Humanitarian Crises. Earlier resolutions, conferences, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 266.15 Td (frameworks have laid important groundwork, even if implementation has often fallen short) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 251.65 Td (of what was promised. Research which instruments are most relevant to UNICEF — including) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 237.15 Td (any prior actions taken by this committee or the bodies it answers to — and consider) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 222.65 Td (honestly why those efforts succeeded, stalled, or failed outright. A strong proposal) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 208.15 Td (builds on this record rather than ignoring it.) Tj ET
