BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 155.95 Td (Delegations facing this topic generally fall into broader groupings shaped by geography,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 141.45 Td (level of development, historical experience, and strategic interest. Rather than) Tj ET
